      en: 'To ensure no local student remains unemployed due to lack of access to quality education and technical/vocational training programs (TEVT). We prepare skilled electrical manpower and competent workforce to meet Nepal\'s growing demands in the electricity sector while fostering holistic development and Nepali cultural values.',
